snippet: A cruise ship attendant confessed to raping a female passenger on Valentine's Day and trying to toss her overboard to cover up the crime, according to an arrest affidavit filed on Tuesday in Miami federal court....

headline.print_headline: Cruise Ship Worker Raped Passenger, Tried to Toss Her Overboard: FBI
headline.main: Cruise Ship Worker Raped Passenger, Tried to Toss Her Overboard: FBI

lead_paragraph: A cruise ship attendant confessed to raping a female passenger on Valentine's Day and trying to toss her overboard to cover up the crime, according to an arrest affidavit filed on Tuesday in Miami federal court.
